data.title: Rational Software Architect 9.0
data.meta_description: IBM Rational Software Architect 9.0 has been made generally available and contains new features as well as fixes for client-reported and internally found defects.
data.text: APARDescription PM56184Popup warnings like: "The license key for this product will expire in..." breaks automatic script. PM64342After performing an automatic merge, sequence diagram interaction use fragments may overlap each other.
